name: GemDetector.ai
description: GemDetector.ai is a Solana-based platform that utilizes multi-agent artificial intelligence to analyze and evaluate newly launched tokens. The platform aggregates and processes real-time trading data, historical price performance, and on-chain fundamentals to provide AI-generated token scores. These scores aim to assist users in identifying potentially undervalued or high-risk assets. The \$GEMAI token serves as the native utility token of the ecosystem, providing access to premium features such as advanced analytics, scoring history, and early alerts for trending tokens. The project is designed to enhance transparency and research quality within the Solana token ecosystem.
